Cognitive Self-Report Questionnaire

back to top

Responses are discrete options, ranging from 1 (Almost Always) to 5 (Hardly Ever), with an additional option of “Does not apply to me”. The overall score is an average of responses, with lower numbers indicating fewer problems with cognition. 13 items are reverse-coded.
